prompts.frontCover: Minimalist flat 2D vector illustration of a cartoon couple on a beach, based on the people in the reference photo. Lao Lao is holding a comically oversized sand shovel and wearing a birthday party hat that is slightly askew. Jordan stands next to her, struggling to hold a giant, wobbly sandcastle cake with one crooked candle on top, looking at her with a funny, exasperated expression. The scene is clean and simple, with a stylized wave line in the background and a cartoon sun wearing sunglasses in the corner. The background is a soft, solid pastel color. Centered in the open space above them, the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao" is written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The overall composition is playful, balanced, and focuses on the humorous interaction between the two characters.
